@API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5174
@Email = testuser_{{$timestamp}}@invoicehub.test
@Password = TestPassword123!

### ==================== REGISTRATION ====================
### 1. Register new account
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "FirstName": "Test",
  "LastName": "User",
  "Email": "{{Email}}",
  "Password": "{{Password}}",
  "ConfirmPassword": "{{Password}}"
}

@authToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0ZXN0IiwiZXhwIjoxNzE2MzY5NjAwfQ.test

###

### ==================== LOGIN ====================
### 2. Login with the new account (extract token)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "{{Email}}",
  "Password": "{{Password}}"
}

###

### ==================== EMAIL VERIFICATION ====================
### 3. Verify email (you need to extract token from verification email)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/verify-email?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ2ZXJpZnkifQ.test
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Resend verification email
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

"{{Email}}"

###

### ==================== PASSWORD RESET ====================
### 5. Forgot password (request reset token)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "{{Email}}"
}

###

### 6. Reset password (use token from forgot-password email)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJyZXNldCJ9.test",
  "NewPassword": "NewPassword456!",
  "ConfirmPassword": "NewPassword456!"
}

###

### ==================== CHANGE PASSWORD ====================
### 7. Change password (requires authentication)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "CurrentPassword": "{{Password}}",
  "NewPassword": "UpdatedPassword789!",
  "ConfirmPassword": "UpdatedPassword789!"
}

###

### ==================== GOOGLE AUTH ====================
### 8. Google authentication (requires Google ID token)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

"eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.test_google_token"

###

### ==================== AI INSIGHTS ====================
### 9. Ask AI a financial question (requires authentication + ManagerUp role)
### ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Update {{authToken}} with Bearer token from login response
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/insights/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

"What is my total revenue and who is my top customer?"

###

### 10. Ask AI another question
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/insights/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

"What are my best-selling products this month?"

###

### 11. Ask AI about expenses
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/insights/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

"How much have I spent on purchases this quarter?"

###

### 12. Generate insights (Admin only)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/insights/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 13. Get all insights
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/insights
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###
